with the proper heritage.

47:32.308 --> 47:34.344
Calavius: Just so.

47:34.519 --> 47:36.680
Relish what you know best.

47:36.855 --> 47:39.813
Leave politics to the men
with breeding for it.

47:39.983 --> 47:41.814
Come, good Solonius.

47:41.985 --> 47:44.567
We have not had occasion
to speak this evening.

47:47.657 --> 47:50.114
The magistrate's response?

47:51.161 --> 47:53.243
To be answered in blood.

49:55.368 --> 49:57.700
(theme music playing )
